originalText.text: I cannot say enough great things about my experience having Michael as our wedding photographer. From the beginning he was so professional but yet fun to ease the stress of our big day. The images he captured are stunning!  He had so many great ideas for pictures, and was great to work with  throughout the whole day! Highly recommend him for any type of event! He even traveled from NY for us. Thanks so much!

originalText.text: I’ve been following Michael’s career for a number of years and have watched him grow into a formidable talent. He’s an extraordinary photographer and approaches all his subjects with a true artist’s eye. From the sublime to the ridiculous Michael captures their essence and spirit while producing not just a beautiful photograph but a true work of art. He’s a great person who exudes joy and a sense of excitement that comes through in his work. And he gives every bit of his talent and expertise to whatever project he is involved in. You will find no one better.

originalText.text: Michael has been my go-to photographer for the last few years.  He has photographed several apartments for me (I am a real estate agent) and always does an amazing job.  He is incredibly meticulous and always goes the extra mile to make sure I get the best shots possible no matter how long it takes.  He also took a professional portrait shot of me at his Midtown East studio and quite frankly, I've never looked so good!  Michael also took some awesome outdoor shots of me that really captured who I am as an artist and healer.  On a side note, Michael also happens to be a stand-up guy... genuinely nice and easy to get along with.

originalText.text: Michael is very professional while making you feel super comfortable in front of the camera. His work is stellar. His drive and passion are evident in his photos and he is a pleasure to work with. We couldn’t be happier with our wedding photos! I would highly recommend him!

originalText.text:
Michael is insanely talented and easy to work with.  He photographs all of my instagram photos and other projects.   Super friendly and quick turnaround time when it comes to delivering photos.
Michael had traveled to Las Vegas with my band to photograph some stellar photos for our website and promotion.  I definitely recommend him for any photography needs! He has also shot video for me as well there’s nothing that Michael can’t achieve creatively through his visual art.  He really seems to connect and understand what client needs and definitely delivers.
